Intentional injuries in the Eastern Mediterranean Region, 1990-2015: findings 
from the Global Burden of Disease 2015 study.

GBD 2015 Eastern Mediterranean Region Intentional Injuries Collaborators.

Collaborators: Moradi-Lakeh M, Charara R, El Bcheraoui C, Khalil I, Afshin A, 
Kassebaum NJ, Collison M, Chew A, Krohn KJ, Daoud F, Colombara D, Graetz N, Kutz 
