Djalalinia S, Doyle KE, Esteghamati A, Faro A, Farvid MS, Fereshtehnejad SM, 
Fischer F, Gebrehiwot TT, Gutiérrez RA, Hafezi-Nejad N, Hamadeh RR, Hamidi S, 
Haro JM, Hendrie D, Hu G, Jonas JB, Keiyoro PN, Khader YS, Khan EA, Khubchandani 
J, Kopec JA, Larson HJ, Latif AA, Leshargie CT, Lunevicius R, Magdy Abd El Razek 
