Obermeyer CM, Ogbo FA, Phillips MR, Pourmalek F, Qorbani M, Radfar A, Rafay A, 
Rahimi-Movaghar A, Rahimi-Movaghar V, Rai RK, Rawaf DL, Rawaf S, Rezaei S, Rezai 
MS, Roshandel G, Safdarian M, Safiri S, Salamati P, Samy AM, Sartorius B, Seedat 
